name: EvilWithinThem.
description:
AnubisFX: EvilWithinThem.
.
[EvilWithinThem.] The darkness lurks all around us. Trapped in a cage tied by a dotted line. Video surveillance captures the torment as twelve eyes lurk the tape. How can this be honorable? Our lives shackled down by ideologies, shoved down our throats and chastised if opposed. Blood on all of our hands, as the blood leaks down our cage, it drips over our consciences. Broken TV screens on repeat reassure with high volume, “Its for a good cause...”. But who’s cause is this truly good for?
